Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:21:00.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}君の横顔が見詰めているのは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.72,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}次の季節だっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:08.10,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}分かってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:11.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}痛いくらいに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:16.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}反射的に笑顔を作る
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:23.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}曖昧な線　揺曳な隙まで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:29.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}無邪気なあざとさで夢を繋いだの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:33.15,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}噓だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:36.04,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}傷だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:41.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}純度だけは固くて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:45.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}ほら　眩しすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.35,0:21:47.41,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}涙　ダイヤモンド
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:53.05,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}きっと終わりが始まってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:22:00.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}ずっと忘れない季節でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:21:00.06,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我凝视着你的侧颜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.72,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}是因为我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:08.10,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}那是下一个季节
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:11.35,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}反射般的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:16.24,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我作出让自己心痛的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:23.34,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}暧昧的线在摇荡的缝隙间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:29.75,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我用天真的小聪明延续着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:33.15,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}尽是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:36.04,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}尽是伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:41.16,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}唯有纯度坚固如昔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:45.16,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}看 那耀眼的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.35,0:21:47.41,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}泪水的钻石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:53.05,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}结局一定开始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:22:00.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\}那一定是永生难忘的季节吧
